    </form>
    
    <div class="form-tips card">
      <h3>ğŸ’¡ Tips for Better Results</h3>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Be specific:</strong> Clear descriptions help agents understand your needs</li>
        <li><strong>Provide context:</strong> Include relevant background information</li>
        <li><strong>Set expectations:</strong> Mention desired output format</li>
        <li><strong>Break down complex tasks:</strong> Large tasks are automatically decomposed</li>
      </ul>
      
